# Previsualization Studio

Production missions with a player spatial loop need a complete **Visual Design Package** before `mission-implementer`.

EP approves the player experience (mental play), not text alone.

Authority: `Documents/04_Production/AIStudio/PrevisualizationStudio/VisualDesignPackage.md` and Production Playbook §12c.

Previs skills communicate design (experience, blockout visuals, storyboard, concept prompts, lighting preview, placement preview). They do not implement Unreal, edit Blueprints, or change Story Canon. Concept work = prompts unless a separate art mission generates images.
